{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571730/extras/Honeycam_2024-10-21_11-22-17.gif?t=1730787190\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The girl and the golem fall into a secret kingdom</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is a rumor that \u201cPanganium,\u201d a substance that can grant wishes, is scattered throughout Sophiatica, the fallen kingdom of alchemists. <br>The little girl Mercuri went on a blind adventure to find Pangenium with her golem, Hando. <br>What secrets and trials will they face? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">You are alone, but you are not alone</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Halchemist, you can control two characters alternately. <br>Don't lock yourself into one character. <br>Mercuri and Hando become a fantastic combination when used alternately! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571730/extras/sample_1.png?t=1730787190\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The girl wielding the book [Mercury]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mercuri is a small and insignificant girl alchemist. <br>Attack your enemies with repeated strikes while swinging a book filled with souls. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fist floating in the air [Hando]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hando is a trustworthy golem that helps the treacherous Mercuri. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571730/extras/Sample.gif?t=1730787190\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Two characters working together: tag action</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hando can fly through the air and pull switches, or explore the map first and then return.<br>With the help of Hando, Mercuri can overcome obstacles and perform clever navigation actions. </p>","background":"https://